<div class="carousel-slide__caption">
                  Vladimir Akimenkov was released in December 2013 after being detained following a protest in Bolotnaya Square, Moscow, Russia. “I want to express my deep gratitude. Your letters influenced my release.”</div>


</div>

</li>


 	

<li class="carousel__slide" data-carousel-slide="2014" style="width: 12.5%;">


